{"tid":1457303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[813離境大堂] 聽日請再一次向世界展示香港人嘅決心！同一地點同一時間見！","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:32:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T13:16:45.000Z","uid":167548,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"c1f15dbee7b30e5551abe441212ac151c251c275","tid":1457303,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:32:04.000Z","msg":"請大家放低今次散水嘅挫折！<br />\n再一次團結起來！<br />\n唔可以被港共睇死我地團結唔起來。<br />\n但是毫無疑問你要大多數嘅香港人陪你留守機場是好難嘅！<br />\n但是只需要繼續<span style=\"color: red;\">每一日同一時間塞入機場！最緊要不遲到！準時！</span>癱瘓離境機場嘅一分一秒都是向政府宣泄怒火嘅成本！<br />\n呢一場是永無止境嘅戰爭！<br />\n<br />\n由今日開始分兩個時段去癱瘓機場！<br />\n<br />\n一、1300 學生撚<br />\n二、2000 放工撚 <br />\n<br />\n不分化！不割席！<br />\n<br />\n利申今日有去機場6點鍾比人水走左，但是聽日下午一時再見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n香港人永不放棄！萬眾一心！</span></span>"},{"pid":"e55b065bea7c69dfcc296c3f3d4857c11be1ebf5","tid":1457303,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:33:57.000Z","msg":"條件許可即入機場<br />\n條件不許可聽日下午一時同埋晚上八時見"},{"pid":"27b350b3b4bad6502e895be1bf9a4546498ff6a3","tid":1457303,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:35:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa2f462df75f01fea6fbb8528f71956786878cb","tid":1457303,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef83284b6510fe4eb61aef527271d121511f80d","tid":1457303,"uid":263336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:35:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd692570ea06f2c8467e7258d05a551b8077370d","tid":1457303,"uid":265256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:35:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d43cc9de2e873b272fb440659b310be1094b5682","tid":1457303,"uid":167548,"like